{
  "stem": "2966.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I told the German, the SS man, that I don't feel good, that I'm sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Must have been crazy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "He gave me a thermometer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And, of course, I had high temperature.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And by a miracle, they had a hospital in camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They put me in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Later, I found out I had typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I was for three days unconscious, completely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I don't remember the three days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "But I was told later that it was a Russian doctor there, also a prisoner, that was giving me some injections and helping me out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "This in any other camp, would have never survived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "In that hospital were mostly Poles and other nationalities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I don't remember any Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Anyway, as I was recuperating there, one day they were handing out packages from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "So, of course, I had my handout, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "But some people started saying, he's a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And I didn't get it, which was not that important.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "I was in a warm, clean place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And I was getting some food, I guess, to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And I didn't have to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "It was pretty good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Then one day they sent you out on a transport walking because it was already January.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "The Russians were pushing them back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had to-- Sachsenhausen, I think, was under Berlin or some-- near Berlin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, I said to the guy there-- there was no German anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was whatever was in charge-- I can't go because I still have temperature.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And truthfully, I did it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they left me alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After a few days, we all went to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That trip, at least I didn't have to walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, those walking trips, that transport that went walking, maybe 10% survived because they walked you for days and days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
